I"{<p>By practicing self compassion you can provide yourself with the need for reassurance and a sense of safety in the absence of another person.</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Notice your critical inner narrative</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Notice the tension in your body created by your critical thoughts and beliefs</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Bring awareness to any areas of tension without resisting them</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Breathe softly to these areas of tension to help you release your built up stress and tension</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Replace your critical thoughts with supportive and reassuring statements</p>
  </li>
</ol>
